    dc:description "FIGURES 58A–I. Hexapopha numerosa sp. nov., male (MPEG 10310; PBI_OON 45963). A–B habitus. A dorsal view. B lateral view. C–E carapace. C dorsal view. D ventral view. E anterior view. F mouthparts, ventral view. G abdomen, ventral view. H–I left palp. H prolateral view. I retrolateral view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
