<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244181>
    dc:description "FIGURES 60A–L. Hexapopha numerosa sp. nov., SEM images. A–I male (MPEG 37036; PBI_OON 46329). J–L female (MPEG 15316; PBI_OON 45438). A habitus, lateral view. B carapace, ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D endites, showing median projections and projection P1. E–F left palp. E prolateral view. F retrolateral view. G–I embolus. G prolateral view. H retrolateral view. I apical view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view (arrow: slit-shaped opening on posterior uterine sclerite). L detail of J, copulatory opening. Abbreviations: as, anterior sclerite; d, duct; mp, median projection; P, projection; vs, ventral surface of distal hook of posterior sclerite." ;
